        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This is equivalent to <computeroutput><ref refid="group__mspi__devicetree_1ga0a91ef9392be4493ede6cea607ee8728" kindref="member">MSPI_DEV_CE_GPIOS_DT_SPEC_GET(DT_DRV_INST(inst))</ref></computeroutput>.</para>
