        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This helper macro check whether <computeroutput>ce_gpios</computeroutput> binding exist first before calling <computeroutput>GPIO_DT_SPEC_GET_BY_IDX</computeroutput> and expand to an array of <ref refid="structgpio__dt__spec" kindref="compound">gpio_dt_spec</ref>.</para>
