</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>an array of <ref refid="structgpio__dt__spec" kindref="compound">gpio_dt_spec</ref> struct corresponding with mspi_dev&apos;s chip enables </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
