        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This is equivalent to <computeroutput><ref refid="group__mspi__devicetree_1ga1ca28d7ead69cd3a5e26198bc6815b54" kindref="member">MSPI_CE_GPIOS_DT_SPEC_GET(DT_DRV_INST(inst))</ref></computeroutput>.</para>
